    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, and it still has that 'new car' feel. It drives like an absolute dream with zero issues at all. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I'm ready for someone else to enjoy this perfect ride. Come take it for a spin, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
