    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from factory-spec bushings and a M-Variable limited-slip differential that provides exceptional corner-exit traction. The exterior retains its original high-gloss finish with no evidence of road rash, while the interior boasts Nappa leather with zero bolster wear or pixel failure in the electronics. Accompanied by a comprehensive service dossier, this is a turn-key specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
